(#### Step 1: Reproducibility and device policy) Tj
T*
(- `set_seed\(\)` sets seeds for Python, NumPy, Torch CPU/CUDA.) Tj
T*
(- Device selection: CUDA if available else CPU.) Tj
T*
(- Mixed precision policy:) Tj
T*
(  - bf16 when `torch.cuda.is_bf16_supported\(\)`) Tj
T*
(  - else fp16 + `GradScaler`) Tj
T*
(  - else fp32 on CPU) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### Step 2: Configuration) Tj
T*
(- `Config` dataclass centralizes run settings.) Tj
T*
(- Notable defaults:) Tj
T*
(  - `model_name="distilbert-base-uncased"`) Tj
T*
(  - `dataset="PolyAI/banking77"`) Tj
T*
