T*
(  - `max_len=64`, `batch_size=32`, `eval_batch=64`) Tj
T*
(  - `epochs=8`, `lr=5e-5`, `warmup_ratio=0.1`) Tj
T*
(  - `weight_decay=0.01`, `max_grad_norm=1.0`) Tj
T*
(  - `val_size=0.10`, `seed=42`) Tj
T*
(  - `ckpt_dir=Path\("checkpoints"\)`, `fig_dir=Path\("figures"\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### Step 3: Data loading and label maps) Tj
T*
(- Loads dataset:) Tj
T*
(  - `raw = load_dataset\(cfg.dataset, revision=cfg.dataset_rev\)`) Tj
T*
(- Constructs label maps from `ClassLabel`:) Tj
T*
(  - `id2label: dict[int, str]`) Tj
T*
(  - `label2id: dict[str, int]`) Tj
T*
(- Data row shape from dataset:) Tj
T*
(  - `{"text": <str>, "label": <int>}`) Tj
T*
(- Committed notebook output shows:) Tj
T*
