T*
() Tj
T*
(#### Step 4: Split and tokenize) Tj
T*
(- Creates validation split from train with stratification:) Tj
T*
(  - `train_test_split\(..., test_size=cfg.val_size, stratify=train_lbls_all, ) Tj
T*
