(Solution outline:) Tj
T*
(- Returns dict with keys `input_ids`, `attention_mask`, `labels`.) Tj
T*
(- This shape matches expected keyword arguments for `AutoModelForSequenceClassification` ) Tj
T*
(forward pass \(`model\(**batch\)`\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
